title: Unable to run tensorboard
body_html:
Hi all,
I'm trying to use tensorboard but I can't find the tensorboard executable in my path. I installed tensorflow with pip.
When trying to run it from source I got the following error

WARNING:root:IOError [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/../tensorflow/external/paper-toggle-button/paper-toggle-button.html' on path /.../tensorflow/external/paper-toggle-button/paper-toggle-button.html

body:
Hi all,
I'm trying to use tensorboard but I can't find the tensorboard executable in my path. I installed tensorflow with pip.
When trying to run it from source I got the following error 

```
WARNING:root:IOError [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/../tensorflow/external/paper-toggle-button/paper-toggle-button.html' on path /.../tensorflow/external/paper-toggle-button/paper-toggle-button.html
```
